Tracks a colored objects using opencv

Requirements:
  opencv 2.2
  python 2.6 or python 2.7


Usage:

Use the color_detector script to find a range of HSV values to track
  ./color_detector.py --help
Use the blob_tracker script to track the object
  ./blob_tracker.py --help


Examples:

Track a green object
  ./blob_tracker.py --green
Track a blue object on video camera at /dev/video1
  ./blob_tracker.py -c 1 --blue
Track a custom HSV value
  ./blob_tracker.py -m "(70, 110, 120)" -x "(105, 255, 255)"
